A '''conflict atlas''', also called '''conflict partiture''', is a [[graphics|graphical]] representation of the development of a particular [[Conflict resolution|conflict]]. The graph shows important events, appointments, and their interlinkage over time. 

This instrument has been mentioned in F. Glasl's book Konfliktmanagement (2004).

